 ↓
Identify Financial Asset
 ↓
Is Asset in ECL Scope? -- No → Exclude
 ↓ Yes
Assess for Significant Increase in Credit Risk (SICR)
 ↓
Classify into Stage (1, 2, 3)
 ↓
Gather PD, LGD, EAD
 ↓
Apply Forward-Looking Adjustments
 ↓
Calculate ECL = PD × LGD × EAD
 ↓
Discount ECL to Present Value
 ↓
Recognize ECL in Financials
 ↓
End